Class HierarchicalElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.model.DefaultRefreshable
      • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.model.Element
        • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.model.HierarchicalElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRefreshable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MenuItem, TreeNode

    public class HierarchicalElement
extends Element
    This class represents a hierarchical structure like Tree or Menu etc.

    History:

    Jun 23, 2014 (Lei Wang) Initial release.
